
pssac2
======

Installation Instructions
-------------------------

 ./configure 
 make
 make install

If ./configure cannot find the required libraries try:

 ./configure --with-gmt=/path/to/gmt --with-netcdf=/path/to/netcdf
 make
 make install

Required Libraries
------------------

 * GMT version 4.2 or higher
 * NetCDF Library (This is required to compile GMT)

Bugs
----

If you find bugs or something does not work as expected, please contact savage@uri.edu 
Yes, there are bugs.